  <para>
    <classname>ExpandByElements</classname> is used as the
    <varname>criterion</varname> parameter of <xref
    linkend="MenuItem-OOF.NodeSelection.Expand_Node_Selection"/>.  It
    expands the current &node; selection by selecting all &nodes; that
    share an &elem; with a &node; that is already selected.  When a
    &skel; contains quadrilateral &elems;,
    <classname>ExpandByElements</classname> may select more &nodes;
    than its colleague <xref
    linkend="RegisteredClass-ExpandBySegments"/> will.
  </para>

  <figure id="Figure-ExpandByElements">
